'''Welspun Group''' (Welspun) ({{BSE|514162}}) is a business conglomerate, manufactures, markets, and exports terry towels, bed sheets, cotton yarn, polyester filament yarn, texturised and Line Pipes<ref name="intoday1"/> based in [[Mumbai]], [[Maharashtra]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://welspun.com/content.asp?FooterID=4 |title=Corporate Office, Address |publisher=welspun.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-04}}</ref> Its other operations includes Steel, Steel pipes, Infrastructure, Energy and Oil & Gas.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://welspun.com/content.asp?Submenu=Y&MenuID=1&SubmenuID=14 |title=About Us |publisher=welspun.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yreach.com/bengaluru/news/welspun-group--industry-well-spun.html |title=Welspun Group - Industry well spun |publisher=Yreach.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-03}}</ref> It also produces [[Terry]] [[Towel]] which is Asia's largest & worlds 2nd largest home textile company [[Welspun India Ltd]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.welspuntowels.com/content.asp?Submenu=Y&MenuID=1&SubmenuID=1 |title=:: Welspun :: |publisher=Welspuntowels.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-03}}</ref> It also second largest manufacturer of large diameter pipes in the world through is subsidiary<ref name="intoday1"/> [[Welspun Corp Ltd]].
